title: 04/29/21 DPS Hour 3 Trey Lance

description:
Dan is joined by Trey Lance, one of the top quarterback prospects in the NFL Draft. Trey talks about his communications with NFL teams during the draft, specifically the San Francisco 49ers, and says he wishes he knew where he would be selected
